doc_summary_long: Staff and regular visitors at Exmoor Zoo in Devon been left heartbroken by the sudden death of a colony of 10 penguins following an outbreak of avian malaria. Exmoor Zoo said 'Hi everyone, we have some very sad news that has taken us all here at the zoo a while to get used to. Exmoor Zoo is greatly saddened to tell everyone that our penguins have all died from a quick and devastating outbreak of avian malaria.
doc_summary_short: Staff and regular visitors at Exmoor Zoo in Devon been left heartbroken by the sudden death of a colony of 10 penguins following an outbreak of avian malaria.
doc_title: Exmoor Zoo penguin colony wiped out by avian malaria
